data.meta_description: Easton Corbin in concert at Johnny's Steaks and Bar-Be-Que in Salado, Texas on Friday, October 13, 2023.
data.text:
Just announced to take the Performance Food Group stage on Friday night, October 13th at Johnny's Steaks and Bar-Be-Que in Salado, Texas is country star Easton Corbin. Corbin has been performing nationwide since getting a record deal in 2009, and the release of his debut album "Easton Corbin" in 2010.

If you have never seen Corbin perform live, you are never going to get a better chance than a Friday night at Johnny's Outback in Salado. There is no better stage, or weather to see a show than in Central Texas on an October night.

What is a concert like at Johnny's Steaks and Bar-Be-Que in Salado?

It is like a professional tailgate with all of your closest family and friends. Shows at Johnny's are always all ages, and the environment is the perfect complement for a cookout of this caliber.

Imagine inviting everyone over for a backyard cookout to enjoy a plate of the best food, the friendliest staff serving the coldest drinks, and you get to enjoy live country all at the same time.

How do you attend a concert at Johnny's Outback in Salado?

You can get your individual tickets and reserved tables of 6 for Johnny's Steaks and Bar-Be-Que here. Johnny's Outback is a cash only event space, and tickets are always available at the door until sold out.

Don't miss your chance to see Easton Corbin while enjoying the coldest drinks and best bar-be-que on a perfect Texas Friday night October 13th.
